    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a very generous drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil </strong>(enough to fully coat the bottom of the pan) over a high heat</p><p>Once the pan is hot, add the <strong>coated jumbo prawns</strong> and cook for 6-7 min, turning occasionally, until the jumbo prawns are browned all over, crispy and cooked through – these are your <strong>jumbo prawn scampi</strong></p>",
