    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a pot over a medium-low heat with a very large knob of<strong> butter</strong></p><p>Once melted, add your <strong>blanched peas</strong>, <strong>chopped mint</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Cook for 1-2 min or until warmed through – these are your <strong>minty peas</strong></p>",
